headline: IQVIA Releases 2024 Sustainability Report
summary: RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C., February 20, 2025--IQVIA (NYSE:IQV), a leading global provider of clinical research services, commercial insights and healthcare intelligence to the life sciences and healthcare industries, has published its 2024 Sustainability Report. The report details IQVIA’s sustainability achievements consistent with its mission to accelerate innovation for a healthier world.
